					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM retains the session lock until the user reestablishes access using established identification and authentication procedures.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to retain the session lock until the user reestablishes access using established identification and authentication procedures.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
