					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM supports the capability to centrally review and analyze audit records from multiple components within the system. If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to support the capability to centrally review and analyze audit records from multiple components within the system.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
