					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM, for PKI-based authentication, validates certificates by constructing a certification path (which includes status information) to an accepted trust anchor.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
