					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM enforces approved authorizations for logical access to information and system resources in accordance with applicable access control policies.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
