				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure all guest VM network communications to be implemented through use of virtual network devices provisioned by the VMM.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
