				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to provide the capability to immediately disconnect or disable remote access to the information system.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
