					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM implements discretionary access controls to allow VMM admins to grant their privileges to other VMM admins.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
