					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM allocates audit record storage capacity to store at least one week's worth of audit records when audit records are not immediately sent to a central audit record storage facility.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
