					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>It is critical for the appropriate personnel to be aware if a VMM is at risk of failing to process audit logs as required. Without a real-time alert, security personnel may be unaware of an impending failure of the audit capability, and system operation may be adversely affected. 

