					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM provides an audit reduction capability that supports on-demand audit review and analysis.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to provide an audit reduction capability that supports on-demand audit review and analysis.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
