					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM, for networked systems, compares internal information system clocks at least every 24 hours with an authoritative time source.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM, for networked systems, to compare internal information system clocks at least every 24 hours with an authoritative time source.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
