					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM protects against or limit the effects of Denial of Service (DoS) attacks by ensuring the VMM is implementing rate-limiting measures on impacted network interfaces.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
